mern setup

install npm global... and install node.js --- using nvm(node version manager)


curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.1/install.sh | bash

nvm install 16

node --version
npm --version

npm install -g npm
npm install -g create-react-app (for global)


setup start from here for any app -----------------------------------------


create folder any name (MERN)

frontend

--->npx create-react-app my-app 

in that folder install ----> npm install react-router-dom


backend


in MERN folder for backend setup

npm init ---> for basic pakage setup

npm install express --> for express installation
npm install -g nodemon -- > server automatically restart for every save for global install pass -g







